## DATA RULES (from manhwa — never break these)
- No duplicate heroes ever — every summon is a unique individual
- Permadeath is permanent — IsAlive=false, no revival
- Synthesis is murder — UI must feel solemn and wrong
- Starting Morale on summon = 40-60 randomized (heroes arrive traumatized)
- HiddenPotential never shown as a number — flavor text only:
  - 0.0–0.3 → "This unit's ceiling appears limited."
  - 0.3–0.7 → "Something stirs beneath the surface."
  - 0.7–1.0 → "The System struggles to quantify this unit."
- Training refines skills only — does NOT increase stats
- System cannot see: hidden skills, emotional state, hero conspiracies

