## KNOWN ISSUES / WATCH OUT FOR
- `SummonView.ShowAffordError` is a Debug.LogWarning placeholder — needs a UI toast later.
- `Resources.Load` for sprites is a Unity anti-pattern — acceptable for now, migrate to Addressables later
- Object pooling needed for Roster (200+ heroes will lag without it) — use ScrollRect + manual pool
- Card portrait renders dark if Image component color is not pure white (255,255,255,255)
- Dead hero "DEAD" overlay must reset in SetupCard() when pooling — or it bleeds to living heroes
- Always run `Tools > Pick Me Up > Setup [X] UI` from the correct scene (Hub open when running Setup Hub UI)
- `starIconPrefab` on SummonView is not wired by editor script — must be done manually in Inspector

